\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch I am a motivated and flexible individual with excellent organisational skills and a consistent high standard of work. I am highly reliable and punctual with }{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}superb}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0} attendance. People describe me as approachable and non-judgemental. I have experience working with a diverse range of individuals in a range of settings. My main skills are: communication, organisation and problem-solving.}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\par}
