\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Employed on a 6-month skills programme where I completed four work placements that provided me with valuable skills and knowledge. I worked as a team with a diverse cohort of peers and developed strong professional relationships. I gained experience from the following work placements:}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\par}
