\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Over a three week period I assisted the Greenscape Tameside team in completing an array of gardening tasks. Through this I gained a better understanding of how to work effectively as a team and how to apply ideas in a constructive manner.}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\par}
