\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch I completed a two week work programme with British Gas at their Stockport and Hattersley locations, in which I actively listened to over ten hours of calls and accompanied an engineer on the job. This experience provided me with a greater perspective on work life and gave me practical experience in working with customers both over the phone and in person.}{\s28\f0\fs24\lang2057{\*\listtag0}\par}
